From: Mete Durlu <meted@linux.ibm.com>
Date: Tue, 14 Jan 2025 17:03:09 +0100
Subject: [PATCH] s390/diag: Add memory topology information via diag310
Git-commit: 0d30871739ab433e114b0058f08b6b1c7b816f7e
Patch-mainline: v6.13
References: jsc#PED-14871

Introduce diag310 and memory topology related subcodes.
Provide memory topology information obtanied from diag310 to userspace
via diag ioctl.

Signed-off-by: Mete Durlu <meted@linux.ibm.com>
Reviewed-by: Heiko Carstens <hca@linux.ibm.com>
Signed-off-by: Alexander Gordeev <agordeev@linux.ibm.com>
Acked-by: Hannes Reinecke <hare@suse.com>
